===Stress===
Stress can fall on any syllable, but tends to be on the first; there is dialectal variation, and minimal pairs distinguished by stress seem to be rare.<ref>Johanna Mattissen, ''Dependent-Head Synthesis in Nivkh: A Contribution to a Typology of Polysynthesis'' (John Benjamins Publishing, 2003; {{ISBN|9027229651}}), pp. 85-86.</ref>

