'''Uruguayans in Cuba''' are people born in [[Uruguay]] who live in [[Cuba]], or Cuban-born people of Uruguayan descent. <!-- As of 2016, there were over 100 Uruguayans living in Cuban territory -->.
During the [[civic-military dictatorship of Uruguay]] (1973-1985) several Uruguayans went into exile in Cuba.
